show.description: The story follows Evelyn Grant, a successful woman trapped in a failing marriage. After ending her three-year union, she hires a handyman to pose as her boyfriend for a day, only to discover that he is a powerful CEO in disguise. This unexpected twist leads to a journey of self-discovery and genuine love.
